WEBVTT

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:31.376
(Applause)

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:33.536
[Great Big Story
in partnership with TED]

00:00:33.560 --> 00:00:36.040
Narrator: They had a big idea
to change the world.

00:00:37.880 --> 00:00:39.816
But they couldn't do it alone.

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:43.216
(Voices overlapping)
So, my wish ... My wish ... I wish ...

00:00:43.240 --> 00:00:45.760
And now here's my wish.

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:47.856
[Torchbearers]

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:50.736
[Ideas in action]

00:00:50.760 --> 00:00:52.160
(Knife chop)

00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:53.976
(Music)

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.856
JO: Food is simple.
It's just raw ingredients.

00:00:56.880 --> 00:00:59.360
But it's the most powerful
killer on the planet.